welcome_message_body: Welcome to Rendsburg, Germany! Known for its picturesque landscapes and rich history, we hope you enjoy your stay and take time to discover the charming streets and unique culture of our beautiful city.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal is the only terminal at Rendsburg Schachtholm Airport and serves all domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Schleswig-jagel Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Schleswig-jagel Airport, mainly used for charter and private flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
